<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="fr"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title><%= title %></title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/luxury-design.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/responsive.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/golden-design.css">
</head><body><header><div class="header-container"><a href="/" class="logo"><% if (logo) { %><img src="<%= logo %>"><% } %><h1>Denisia Bijoux</h1></a></div></header><main><div class="confirmation-container container"><div class="success-icon"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></div><h1>Commande confirmée !</h1><p>Votre commande <strong>#<%= order.orderNumber %></strong> a été enregistrée avec succès.</p><div class="order-summary"><h3>Détails de la commande</h3><% order.items.forEach(item => { %><div class="summary-row"><span><%= item.productName %> x<%= item.quantity %></span><span><%= item.subtotal.toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA</span></div><% }) %><div class="summary-row"><span>Livraison</span><span><%= order.deliveryPrice.toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA</span></div><div class="summary-row"><span>Total</span><span><%= order.total.toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA</span></div><p style="margin-top: 2rem;">Un email de confirmation a été envoyé à <strong><%= order.customer.email %></strong></p></div><a href="/" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Retour à l'accueil</a></div></main><script src="/js/main.js"></script>  <script src="/js/mobile.js"></script>
</body></html>
